    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When a creature within 30 feet of you hits as a result of your Strike like Iron or when one of your Merit dice is expended for an Exploit by a creature other than you, you can take a Reaction to make a weapon attack or Unarmed Strike. The attack must be made within range of your weapon or Unarmed Strike. Your weapon attacks and Unarmed Strikes have their Critical Hit threshold expanded by one as part of this Reaction. If you hit with this attack you deal extra damage equal to your Charisma modifier (minimum of 1).</p>",
